Package: notes
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libqt5widgets5, libqt5sql5, libqt5sql5-sqlite
Description: Modern note taking application
 A fast, native Linux note-taking application built with C++ and Qt.
 Features include:
  * Three-pane layout (folders, notes list, editor)
  * Markdown editing with live syntax highlighting
  * Dark theme with Apple Notes-inspired design
  * Folder and note management
  * SQLite storage for persistence
  * Auto-bullet and auto-numbering
  * Checkbox toggling and indentation support
